This paper deals with the optimization of status update policies for an energy harvesting sensor, which involves the management of information freshness and energy constraints. This topic is closely related to information theory (cs.IT) and networked systems (cs.NI), as well as control and optimization (cs.SY), machine learning (cs.LG), and mathematical analysis (cs.MA).
